# NTCSS II Devices File
#
# Add a new line for each device connected to this host.  The second
# item in each line must be the name of the "no rewind" device file
# while the third item is reserved for the generic name of the device.
# Use the following lines as examples:
#
# DRIVE  /dev/rmt/0mn  4 mm DAT
# DRIVE  /dev/nrst1    Streamer Tape Drive
#
DRIVE /dev/rmt/4mmn 4 mm DAT
DRIVE /dev/rmt/8mmn 8 mm DAT
FILE  /h/USERS/ntcssii/backups/NTCSSII.BAK NTCSS BACKUP TO DISK

